Description: The captivating charm and the fiery spirit of the woman of today is captured by the house of Revlon and imbued in the tones of Charlie Red, a classic revisited and colored in contemporary hues. She is a woman who is feminine yet the spirit with which she tackles challenges and curveballs that life throws at her leave you open mouthed with admiration. The mass premium comforts her when she is most vulnerable and reinstates her faith in herself. If you are a lover of classic fragrances that linger in the air and colors you memory of a special day with family, this Eau de Cologne is a tasteful addition to complete your outfit. The floral woody undertones of the perfume stand testimony to your smiles and tears throughout. Invoking the timeless charm of luxurious irresistibility, accords of delicious blackcurrant buds, light orange flower, violet leaf and nasturtium present you with a playful opening note that leaves you yearning for more. The exotic accords of ylang ylang commingle with the luscious red plum apricot in the middle notes as velvety rose, soothing jasmine and Lily of the Valley spread their redolence in the heart which is the essence of the fragrance. As the fire dies down and a soothing sense of satisfaction spreads through the air, light steps of tonka beans, ambery and heliotrope flower steal a moment from eternity as the mouth-watering sweetness of vanilla lead you along the trail of the dry down. Launched in 1993, Revlon Charlie Red is presented in a tasteful flacon that is charming yet simple, very much like the woman it adorns. Seal the memories of beautiful day and ease through life on the happiness that overpowers you with the mild company of Revlon Charlie Red EDC.

Title: Christian Dior Fahrenheit Eau de Parfum  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: The FragranceA harmony of opposites to combine strength and elegance.The fragrance dons a vibrant and sensual accord, featuring violet and leather accents enhanced with Bourbon vanilla absolute.The irresistible appeal of a unique fragrance heightened by precious ingredients.Fragrance NotesTop Notes - Sicilian mandarinAll Mediterranean countries grow mandarin trees, but the best mandarins are produced in Sicily. The different colors of mandarin, yellow, green and red, correspond to the different stages of ripeness. Essence of mandarin is a citrus note, offering fragrances a fresh and fruity accent. Mandarin is an exotic top note.Heart Notes - Violet - Leather accordThe leaves of the violet produce a unique and powerful fragrance with green, vegetable and ever so slightly flowery notes. The sensual violet is a surprising heart note in Fahrenheit.The leather note was originally created to imitate the smell of the Russian leather used to make hussars' boots. Their soft leather was tanned using birch bark. Perfumers recreated these burnt, smoky, birch, styrax and cade notes delivering an exotic, enchanting effect. It features as a heart note in Fahrenheit.Base Notes - Bourbon vanilla accordThe white vanilla flowers produce a fruit that ripens in 8 to 9 months. Vanilla beans are harvested just before they are ripe and undergo a ripening process for 34 months. Their fragrance develops and vanilla crystals form. Vanilla gives off its sweet and spicy accords.

Description: She is pure from within, she carries with her an aura of chastity that tugs at your heart strings. Nike adorns her innocence with Pure, the fragrance that reminds you of a time when you were unsullied and your soul was spotless. The fresh notes of the Eau de Toilette has floral and fruity edges that lend depth and character to the fragrance. Wrap yourself in the warm embrace of Nike Pure EDT which is presented in a transparent flacon with blue and orange accents. The same chastity is carried on in the Nike Pure Deo Spray, the joy and freshness of early morning dew gracing the full blooms in a rose garden in spring. The soothing fragrance lends a natural glow to your persona as you strut around with the confidence of someone who has found the solution to perspiration. Enclosed in a tall blue flacon with grey and and orange accents that complement the flacon of the Eau de Toilette, Nike Pure Deo Spray is your answer to all the freshness in the world. This Nike Gift Set of two mass premium fragrances from the Pure range is the perfect gift for the woman in your life.
